%                                                        
%[[ 
Some natural numbers; a demo of [[Project:Literate Twelf|Literate Twelf]]. 
%]]
%[[ ## Syntax %]]
%sort nat %.
%term z nat %.
%term s %pi nat %-> nat %.
%[[ ## Judgments %]]
%[[ ### Equality %]]
%sort id-nat {_ nat} {_ nat} %.
%term id-nat/refl id-nat N N %.
%[[ ### Addition === | %]]
%sort plus {_ nat} {_ nat} {_ nat} %.
%term plus/z plus z N N %.
%term plus/s %pi (plus N1 N2 N3) %-> (plus (s N1) N2 (s N3)) %.
%[[ Now we can see what it looks like to run a query: |check=decl %]]
%solve _ : plus (s (s (s z))) (s (s z)) N %.
%[[
